20industry%20is%20fierce%2C%20as%20hedge%20funds%20and%20other%20asset%20managers%20have%20even%20issued%20incremental%20equity%20or%20long-term%20awards%2C%20Connors%20said%20%E2%80%94%20they%20often%20range%20from%20%24500%2C000%20to%20%241%20million%2C%20typically%20vesting%20across%20three%20to%20four%20years.%20Some%20firms%20have%20offered%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20upfront%20sign-on%20grants%2C%26quot%3B%20often%20in%20excess%20of%20%24200%2C000%2C%20delivered%20off%20the%20bat%20as%20cash%20or%20equity%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-shape-4-investment-banking-careers-ecm-dcm-advisory-trading-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFor%20banks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%2C%20it%20has%20created%20a%20conundrum%20%E2%80%94%20how%20to%20extend%20big-ticket%20offers%20while%20adhering%20to%20their%20often%20rigid%2C%20standardized%20compensation%20bands.%20Hiring%20managers%20are%20forking%20over%20%26quot%3Bsome%20uncomfortable%20hiring%20packages%26quot%3B%20which%20are%20vaulting%20recipients%20into%20%26quot%3Ba%20completely%20different%20stratosphere%2C%26quot%3B%20Bulkoski%20explained%2C%20noting%20that%20top%20compensation%20packages%20for%20senior-level%20AI%20leaders%20are%20reaching%20the%20high%20seven-%20and%20even%20eight-figure%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNobody's%20leaving%20for%20less%20than%2030%25%26quot%3B%20pay%20increases%20if%20they're%20coming%20from%20companies%20where%20they're%20already%20%26quot%3Bheads-down%20and%20doing%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BNo%20one's%20going%20to%20move%20for%20the%20historical%2010%2C%2015%2C%20or%20even%2020%25%20bump%20in%20compensation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228e151ae5-c703-4950-858e-004fb39cf996%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaking%20money%20moves%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-ai-job-career-transition-pivot-startups-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20hiring%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20financial%20services%20industry%20grew%20in%202025%20to%2010%20times%20its%20level%20at%20the%20start%20of%20January%202022%2C%20according%20to%20an%20analysis%20by%20workforce%20data%20provider%20Revelio%20Labs.%20To%20assemble%20the%20data%2C%20Revelio%20examined%20finance%20job%20postings%20for%20roles%20like%20%26quot%3BAI%20engineer%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bmachine%20learning%20engineer%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bcomputer%20vision%20engineer%2C%26quot%3B%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESix%20of%20the%20largest%20US%20banks%20%E2%80%94%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-jpmorgan-office-tower-270-park-avenue-gym-membership-amenities-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJPMorgan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%2C%20and%20Morgan%20Stanley%20%E2%80%94%20have%20collectively%20posted%20more%20than%202%2C000%20AI%20roles%20in%20the%20past%2012%20months%2C%20Revelio's%20data%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20surging%20demand%20for%20AI%20talent%20is%20driving%20paychecks%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20salary%20for%20AI%20professionals%20in%20finance%2C%20excluding%20C-suite%20roles%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehad%20risen%20to%20about%20%24180%2C000%20from%20%24142%2C000%20in%202020.%20That%20increase%20of%20more%20than%2025%25%20puts%20them%20on%20par%20with%20what%20conventional%20tech%20firms%20tend%20to%20pay%20for%20these%20roles%2C%20Revelio%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJPMorgan%20and%20Morgan%20Stanley%20declined%20to%20comment%2C%20while%20others%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20have%20seen%20with%20banks%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%20is%20they've%20had%20to%20really%20reframe%20and%20reimagine%20those%20comp%20ranges%2C%20especially%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20this%20type%20of%20talent%2C%26quot%3B%20Ben%20Hodzic%2C%20head%20of%20North%20America%20at%20the%20recruiting%20firm%20Selby%20Jennings%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20That's%20especially%20true%20as%20they're%20coming%20up%20against%20multistrategy%20hedge%20funds%20and%20high-frequency%20systematic%20trading%20firms%20that%20are%20%26quot%3Bpaying%20whatever%20they%20need%20to%20pay%20to%20get%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226e3993ff-9d25-4b79-b8a1-0044c6e50638%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeat%20at%20the%20table%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20money%20alone%20isn't%20enough%2C%20insiders%20said.%20These%20technologists%20also%20want%20something%20else%3A%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsiders%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgemini-3-launch-google-ai-race-chatgpt-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20AI%20race%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20elevated%20the%20voices%20of%20technology%20chiefs%20at%20banks%20and%20asset%20managers%2C%20giving%20them%20a%20perch%20at%20powerful%20tables%20that%20steer%20firms'%20overall%20strategy.%20Bulkoski%20said%20that%2C%20for%20prospective%20AI%20chiefs%2C%20wielding%20greater%20levels%20of%20influence%20in%20the%20boardroom%20alongside%20other%20C-suite%20leaders%20is%20an%20appealing%20prospect%20unto%20itself.%20%26quot%3BIt%20could%20trump%20another%20number%20on%20the%20sheet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nature%20of%20the%20work%20is%20attracting%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-startup-hebbia-wall-street-investment-banking-work-demo-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebroad%20swathe%20of%20professionals%3C%2Fa%3E%20eager%20to%20exploit%20the%20breach.%20%26quot%3BGo%20on%20LinkedIn%20and%20look%20at%20the%20number%20of%20people%20who%20just%20changed%20their%20title%20from%20data%20scientist%20to%20AI%20scientist%2C%26quot%3B%20Bulkoski%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20kind%20of%20unbelievable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECandidates%20for%20senior-level%20roles%20are%20skewing%20younger%2C%20he%20continued.%20Some%20AI-savvy%20talent%20in%20their%20early-%20to%20mid-20s%20are%20pulling%20high-six%20to%20seven-figure%20offers%2C%20he%20said.%20To%20suss%20out%20who%20is%20a%20fit%20and%20who%20isn't%2C%20Bulkoski%20said%20his%20team%20assesses%20%26quot%3Bwhether%20they%20have%20a%20real%20track%20record%26quot%3B%20of%20constructing%20original%20AI%20or%20machine%20learning%20products%20at%20scale%2C%20and%20if%20they%20can%20channel%20that%20knowledge%20into%20creating%20commercial%20or%20operational%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20are%20in%20the%20early%20phases%20of%20developing%20executive%20maturity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20the%20best%20of%20them%20can%20already%20influence%20senior%20leaders%20by%20grounding%20every%20conversation%20in%20architecture%2C%20data%2C%20and%20measurable%20impact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22786c64ec-dfdb-4f7c-a393-d360d0842f41%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20ladder%20up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20access%20to%20the%20board%20and%20stepped-up%20influence%20and%20responsibility%2C%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-juniors-may-manage-bots-execs-say-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWall%20Street%20insiders%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20betting%20they%20can%20offer%20something%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20generally%20can't%3A%20a%20steadier%2C%20more%20clearly%20defined%20climb%20up%20the%20professional%20ranks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20tech%20firms%20consolidating%20and%20fears%20of%20an%20AI%20bubble%20mounting%2C%20recruiters%20say%20some%20technologists%20are%20increasingly%20drawn%20to%20the%20stability%20and%20hierarchy%20that%20the%20financial%20services%20industry%20is%20known%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20been%20a%20lot%20less%20volatility%20with%20jobs%20in%20the%20finance%20industry%20compared%20to%20the%20tech%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Selby%20Jennings'%20Hodzic%2C%20adding%20that%20finance%20offers%20a%20more%20well-worn%2C%