0developers%20tap%20into%20powerful%20models%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fanthropic%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnthropic's%3C%2Fa%3E%20Claude%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-vibes-ai-internal-documents-show-daily-active-users-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta's%3C%2Fa%3E%20Llama.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20over%20the%20summer%2C%20Bedrock%20hit%20%26quot%3Bcritical%20capacity%20constraints%26quot%3B%20that%20drove%20some%20customers%20to%20rival%20services%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-offers-voluntary-buyouts-uk-employees-vep-ai-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E's%20cloud%20service%2C%20according%20to%20an%20internal%20July%20document%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shortages%20led%20to%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20lost%20or%20delayed%20revenue.%20Epic%20Games%20shifted%20a%20%2410%20million%20Fortnite%20project%20to%20Google%20Cloud%20after%20AWS%20failed%20to%20provide%20enough%20quota%20for%20Bedrock%2C%20according%20to%20the%20document.%20(Quota%20limits%20control%20how%20much%20intelligence%20customers%20can%20access%20via%20AI%20cloud%20services).%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOil%20trader%20Vitol%20weighed%20moving%20some%20projects%20away%20from%20AWS%2C%20a%20decision%20that%20risked%20a%20%243.5%20million%20revenue%20hit%20amid%20%26quot%3Bprolonged%20quota%20approvals%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20document%20also%20warned.%20Other%20customers%2C%20including%20Atlassian%20and%20GovTech%20Singapore%2C%20were%20waiting%20on%20quota%20increases%20this%20summer%2C%20delaying%20at%20least%20%2452.6%20million%20in%20projected%20sales%2C%20the%20document%20also%20disclosed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBedrock%20was%20%26quot%3Bexperiencing%20critical%20capacity%20constraints%20that%20are%20threatening%20customer%20adoption%20and%20potentially%20causing%20substantial%20revenue%20loss%20across%20multiple%20industries%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20July%20document%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fallout%20underscores%20the%20financial%20toll%20of%20AWS's%20capacity%20crunch%2C%20and%20it%20explains%20why%20the%20biggest%20cloud%20companies%20are%20rushing%20to%20build%20as%20many%20AI%20data%20centers%20as%20possible%20right%20now.%20High%20demand%20is%20a%20good%20thing%2C%20but%20if%20you%20can't%20satisfy%20this%20and%20customers%20go%20to%20rivals%2C%20that's%20a%20frustrating%20problem.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20Amazon%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-amazons-hardcore-culture-reset-day-1-roots-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAndy%20Jassy%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20repeatedly%20stressed%20the%20need%20to%20ramp%20up%20cloud%20infrastructure%2C%20particularly%20AI%20chips%20and%20data%20center%20power.%20It's%20unclear%20whether%20the%20company%20has%20fully%20resolved%20these%20issues.%20Three%20current%20and%20former%20employees%20said%20the%20capacity%20crunch%20remained%20one%20of%20AWS's%20top%20concerns%20through%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20said%20Bedrock%20is%20%26quot%3Bexperiencing%20rapid%20growth%26quot%3B%20and%20AWS%20is%20adding%20capacity%20to%20meet%20that%20demand.%20Reviewing%20customer%20feedback%20is%20a%20core%20part%20of%20Amazon's%20culture%2C%20which%20helps%20the%20company%20improve%20its%20products%20and%20services%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20Amazon%2C%20we're%20vocally%20self-critical%20because%20that's%20how%20we%20drive%20continuous%20improvement%20and%20deliver%20better%20results%20for%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BThis%20internal%20candor%20is%20a%20feature%20of%20our%20culture%2C%20not%20a%20flaw.%20We're%20grateful%20for%20all%20customer%20feedback%E2%80%94including%20challenges%20they%20encounter%E2%80%94because%20it%20helps%20us%20make%20Bedrock%20even%20better%2C%20and%20that's%20exactly%20how%20you%20build%20a%20scalable%2C%20sustainable%20business%20that%20serves%20customers%20well%20over%20the%20long%20term.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Google%20spokesperson%20declined%20to%20comment.%20Representatives%20for%20Anthropic%20and%20Epic%20Games%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227ad24bb0-9e31-4ee1-8c21-aabc99949563%5C%22%3E'Accelerating%20capacity'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EExpanding%20data%20center%20capacity%2C%20as%20with%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-data-centers-us-chips-electricity-power-crunch-shortage-goldman-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecloud%20providers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20one%20of%20AWS's%20top%20priorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20October%20earnings%20call%2C%20Jassy%20said%20AWS%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bfocused%20on%20accelerating%20capacity%20the%20last%20several%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20more%20than%203.8%20gigawatts%20of%20power%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20more%20than%20any%20other%20cloud%20provider.%20AWS%20has%20doubled%20its%20power%20capacity%20since%202022%20and%20plans%20to%20double%20it%20again%20by%202027%2C%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJassy%20added%20that%20Amazon%20will%20remain%20%26quot%3Bvery%20aggressive%26quot%3B%20in%20scaling%20up%20capacity%20to%20meet%20booming%20demand%2C%20noting%20that%20AWS%20can%20monetize%20new%20infrastructure%20almost%20immediately.%20Bedrock%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20already%20showing%20potential%20to%20grow%20as%20large%20as%20EC2%2C%20one%20of%20AWS's%20most%20successful%20cloud%20products%20and%20a%20key%20profit%20engine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20Bedrock's%20shortages%20may%20stem%20from%20prioritizing%20large%20clients.%20In%20October%2C%20Jassy%20said%20most%20of%20Bedrock's%20workloads%20run%20on%20AWS's%20in-house%20AI%20chip%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartups-amazon-ai-chips-less-competitive-nvidia-gpus-trainium-aws-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrainium%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20that%20usage%20so%20far%20has%20come%20mainly%20from%20%26quot%3Ba%20small%20number%20of%20very%20large%20customers.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20that%20more%20mid-sized%20companies%20are%20expected%20to%20adopt%20the%20next-generation%20Trainium%20in%20the%20coming%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20is%20expected%20to%20reveal%20more%20details%20about%20Bedrock%20and%20its%20broader%20cloud%20strategy%20during%20its%20annual%20re%3AInvent%20conference%20in%20early%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amazon%20CEO%20Andy%20Jassy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6900022f0be9845f2dc532bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmazon%20CEO%20Andy%20Jassy%3Cp%3ENoah%20Berger%2FNoah%20Berger%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2245f6d5cd-5979-4255-b8f8-5bae2a25ddc9%5C%22%3E'Urgent%20need'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20July%20AWS%20document%20said%20the%20capacity%20crunch%20was%20hitting%20customers%20across%20industries%2C%20including%20finance%2C%20gaming%2C%20and%20tech.%20Companies%20such%20as%20HelloFresh%2C%20Zalando%2C%20and%20Ryanair%20were%20among%20those%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20%26quot%3Bslow%20capacity%20approval%20and%20denial%20of%20spiky%20workload%20requests%26quot%3B%20prevented%20firms%20like%20Stripe%2C%20Robinhood%2C%20and%20Vanguard%20from%20moving%20AI%20workloads%20from%20Anthropic%20to%20Bedrock%2C%20the%20document%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20constraints%20are%20forcing%20customers%20to%20explore%20alternative%20providers%20like%20GCP%2C%20OpenAI%2C%20and%20Anthropic%2C%20signaling%20an%20urgent%20need%20for%20AWS%20to%20address%20its%20Bedrock%20service%20quota%20and%20performance%20challenges%20to%20maintain%20competitive%20positioning%20in%20the%20rapidly%20evolving%20GenAI%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20document%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuota%20limits%20in%20Bedrock%20are%20based%20on%20how%20many%20AI%20tokens%20you%20can%20process%20in%20a%20minute%2C%20or%20the%20number%20of%20API%20calls%20you%20can%20make%20in%20a%20given%20time%20period.%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jensen-huang-ai-factory-tokens-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETokens%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20how%20AI%20models%20break%20queries%20down%20into%20digestible%20data%20chunks.%20Industry%20pricing%20is%20based%20on%20how%20many%20tokens%20are%20processed.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fwhat-is-an-api%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAPIs%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20application%20programming%20interfaces%2C%20a%20common%20way%20applications%20share%20data).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20weeks%2C%20investors%20have%20grown%20uneasy%20over%20the%20tech%20industry's%20massive%20AI%20spending%2C%20with%20fears%20of%20a%20potential%20bubble%20weighing%20on%20markets.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon's%20AI%20capacity%20issues%20are%20a%20double-edge%20sword%20here.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20these%20challenges%20suggest%20customer%20demand%20is%20still%20very%20strong.%20On%20the%20other%2C%20it's%20another%20reason%20for%20big%20tech%20companies%20to%20keep%20spending%20heavily%2C%20potentially%20fueling%20the%20AI%20bubble%20even%20more.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20has%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20pour%20%24125%20billion%20into%20capital%20expenditures%20this%20year%2C%20and%20even%20more%20in%202026.%20AWS%20revenue%20climbed%20to%20%2433%20billion%20last%20quarter%2C%20up%2020%25%20year%20over%20year%2C%20marking%20its%20fastest%20growth%20since%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2266e3e828-5880-49ae-883e-36f6deeabd31%5C%22%3EPerformance%20issues%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20just%20capacity%20woes%20driving%20customer%20workloads%20away%20from%20Bedrock.%20Latency%20and%20missing%20features%20also%20played%20a%20major%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECustomers%20using%20Anthropic's%20Claude%20models%20through%20Bedrock%20opted%20to%20switch%20to%20Anthropic's%20own%20platform%20or%20Google%20Cloud%20because%20of%20%26quot%3Bongoing%20capacity%2C%20latency%2C%20and%20feature%20parity%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20July%20AWS%20document.%20Companies%20such%20as%20Figma%2C%20Intercom%2C%20and%20Wealthsimple%20were%20among%20those%20migrating%20their%20workloads%20%26quot%3Bdue%20to%20one%20or%20several%20of%20these%20challenges.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UK's%20Government%20Digital%20Service%20considered%20a%20move%20to%20Microsoft's%20cloud%20because%20Anthropic's%20Claude%203.7%20Sonnet%20model%20ran%20slower%20on%20Bedrock%2C%20the%20document%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThomson%20Reuters%20also%20chose%20Google%20Cloud%20over%20Bedrock%20for%20its%20CoCounsel%20AI%20product%20after%20finding%20AWS's%20service%20was%2015%25%20to%2030%25%20slower%20and%20lacked%20key%20government%20compliance%20certifications%2C%20the%20document%20showed.%20In%20May%2C%20executives%20raised%20these%20concerns%20with%20AWS%20leadership%2C%20including%20CEO%20Matt%20Garman%20and%20compute%20VP%20Dave%20Brown%2C%20leading%20both%20companies%20to%20agree%20to%20monthly%20review%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoel%20Hron%2C%20CTO%20of%20Thomson%20Reuters%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20company%20recently%20moved%20%26quot%3Bone%20component%20of%20an%20AI%20workload%20to%20Google%20Cloud%20to%20prioritize%20latency.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20that%20Thomson%20Reuters%20still%20runs%20substantial%20workloads%20on%20AWS%20and%20Anthropic%20as%20part%20of%20its%20multi-model%2C%20multi-cloud%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22437a17ce-fa6f-4468-b7cc-6a7a5e6a9e25%5C%22%3E'Increasing%20competition'%20from%20Google%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20July%20AWS%20document%20also%20noted%20that%20Bedrock%20was%20losing%20ground%20to%20Google's%20Gemini%20models%2C%20which%20boast%20five%20to%20six%20times%20larger%20quota%20limits%20and%2C%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20better%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20comparing%20accessing%20Claude%20via%20Bedrock%20against%20Gemini%20Pro%2C%20the%20internal%20report%20said%20the%20Google%20model%20outperformed%20%26quot%3Bacross%20multiple%20benchmarks.%26quot%3B%20The%20document%20also%20noted%20that%20Gemini%20Flash%2C%20a%20smaller%2C%20cheaper%20Google%20model%2C%20%26quot%3Bdelivers%20comparable%20quality%20at%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20cost.%26quot%3B%20(And%20this%20was%20before%20Google's%20Gemini%203%20launch%2C%20which%20improved%20AI%20performance%20further%20for%20the%20internet%20giant).%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20startups%20jumped%20ship%20because%20of%20this.%20Financial%20startup%20TainAI%20shifted%2040%25%20of%20its%20Claude%20workloads%20from%20Bedrock%20to%20Gemini%20Flash%2C%20saving%20%2485%2C000%20a%20day%2C%20while%20Hotel%20Planner%20was%20planning%20to%20move%20to%20Google%20Cloud%20or%20OpenAI%2C%20the%20document%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20broader%20concern%2C%20according%20to%20the%20document%2C%20is%20that%20AWS%20lacked%20a%20cohesive%20product%20vision%20for%20AI%20inference%2C%20the%20main%20space%20in%20which%20Bedrock%20competes.%20Rivals%20such%20as%20Databricks%2C%20FireworksAI%2C%20and%20Nvidia's%20Dynamo%20were%20quickly%20pulling%20ahead%2C%20it%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20a%20clear%20strategy%20or%20compelling%20long-term%20vision%2C%20AWS%20risked%20missing%20out%20on%20one%20of%20the%20most%20lucrative%20opportunities%20in%20the%20AI%20market%2C%20it%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20still%20missing%20an%20inspiring%20long-term%20vision%20and%20a%20holistic%20strategy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20document%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3