s%20Insider%20at%20the%20company's%20Stockholm%20office%20that%20the%20interceptor%20is%20designed%20with%20simplicity%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20police%20officer%20should%20be%20able%20to%20easily%20carry%20several%20Kreuger-100XRs%20in%20a%20backpack%20and%20then%20launch%20them%20from%20a%20handheld%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20testing%2C%20we%20can%20either%20throw%20it%20like%20a%20dart%20or%20use%20a%20catapult%2C%26quot%3B%20Holzapfel%20said%2C%20balancing%20a%20prototype%20on%20his%20fingers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20only%20someone%20with%20an%20exceptionally%20strong%20arm%20can%20hurl%20the%20interceptor%20fast%20enough%20for%20an%20effective%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2268d6cdaa-c639-4969-b860-975a51597c07%5C%22%3EMaking%20cheap%20counters%20to%20drone%20swarms%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHolzapfel%20said%20the%20Kreuger-100XR's%20main%20cost%20goes%20toward%20two%20key%20components.%20The%20first%20is%20a%20camera%20that%20enables%20the%20interceptor%20to%20autonomously%20acquire%20its%20target%2C%20while%20the%20second%20is%20an%20optional%20250-gram%20explosive%20warhead%20for%20destroying%20larger%20aircraft%20such%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-has-version-iranian-shahed-that-russia-uses-attack-ukraine-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EShahed-136%20attack%20drone%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20cheaper%20version%20with%20a%20laser%20seeker%2C%20in%20lieu%20of%20a%20camera%2C%20is%20also%20planned.%20It%20will%20require%20a%20laser%20designator%2C%20whether%20operated%20by%20a%20human%20or%20an%20autonomous%20device%2C%20to%20track%20its%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20XR%2C%20its%20wings%20also%20allow%20us%20to%20loiter%2C%20so%20we%20don't%20need%20a%20straight-shot%20scenario%2C%26quot%3B%20Holzapfel%20said.%20With%20a%20radio%20connection%2C%20the%20interceptor%20is%20designed%20to%20remain%20airborne%20for%20at%20least%2020%20minutes%20before%20acquiring%20a%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20prototype%20of%20the%20Kreuger-100XR%20takes%20flight%20after%20being%20launched%20by%20a%20catapult.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691fd3d689026fbb4d0e1efc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221425%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20prototype%20of%20the%20Kreuger-100XR%20takes%20flight%20after%20being%20launched%20by%20a%20catapult.%3Cp%3ENordic%20Air%20Defence%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20sense%2C%20the%20Kreuger-100XR%20can%20act%20like%20an%20autonomous%20drone%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20NAD's%20long-term%20vision.%20A%20cheap%2C%20fire-and-forget%20interceptor%20could%20become%20a%20fundamental%20defense%20against%20enemy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-could-overwhelm-us-forces-with-drone-swarms-report-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edrone%20swarms%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20anticipated%20threat%20for%20which%20militaries%20around%20the%20world%20are%20preparing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20economy%20of%20war%20is%20at%20such%20a%20point%20that%20it's%20about%20scalability%2C%26quot%3B%20Holzapfel%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20are%20being%20attacked%20by%20a%20swarm%20of%20drones%2C%20we%20need%20a%20swarm%20of%20counter-drones.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20drone%20manufacturers%20have%20also%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-interceptor-drones-air-defense-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edeveloping%20their%20own%20interceptors%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20quadcopters%20capable%20of%20flying%20fast%20enough%20to%20catch%20the%20Shahed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20they%20tend%20to%20be%20slower%20or%20more%20expensive%2C%26quot%3B%20Holzapfel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20interceptor%20drones%20use%20four%20motors%2C%20which%20can%20be%20more%20costly%2C%20the%20Kreuger-100XR%20uses%20a%20single%20prop%20engine%2C%20helping%20NAD%20drive%20down%20costs%20and%20increase%20the%20device's%20speed%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222607%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20propeller%20of%20a%20prototype%20of%20the%20Kreuger-100%20can%20be%20seen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691c93cfabd5e944effaf03e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221955%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Kreuger-100%20and%20its%20XR%20variant%20use%20single%20propellers.%20This%20is%20a%20prototype%20of%20the%20drone%20interceptor.%3Cp%3EMatthew%20Loh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20it%20may%20be%20some%20time%20until%20a%20Kreuger-100XR%20counterswarm%20becomes%20a%20reality.%20Holzapfel%20said%20NAD%20is%20still%20working%20on%20friend-or-foe%20programming%20to%20prevent%20multiple%20interceptors%20from%20targeting%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d8644607-72df-46cc-b216-41df54d79cfa%5C%22%3EShaheds%20and%20recon%20drones%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20is%20positioning%20the%20Kreuger-100XR%20to%20fight%20the%20Shahed%2C%20which%20Russia%20has%20been%20using%20in%20droves%20to%20bombard%20Ukrainian%20cities%20and%20overwhelm%20air%20defenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKyiv%20also%20needs%20more%20defensive%20options%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-unjammable-fiber-optic-drone-keep-pace-russia-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eunjammable%2C%20small%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20use%20cable%20connections%2C%20as%20well%20as%20medium-range%20reconnaissance%20drones%20like%20the%20Orlan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENAD%20plans%20to%20conduct%20trials%20in%20Ukraine%20soon%2C%20but%20has%20yet%20to%20test%20its%20product%20in%20battle.%20An%20operational%20altitude%20of%201%2C000%20meters%20will%20also%20be%20a%20challenge%20for%20the%20Kreuger-100XR%2C%20because%20many%20Russian%20Shaheds%20and%20Gerbera%20decoys%20are%20known%20to%20cruise%20at%202%2C000%20meters%20or%20above%20before%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-shahed-dive-bomb-shahed-kilometers-avoid-small-arms-fire-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ediving%20down%20at%20their%20targets.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Ukrainian%20interceptor%20drone%20hunts%20down%20a%20Russian%20Shahed%20in%20a%20video%20shared%20by%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691cccd989026fbb4d0de355%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221604%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Ukrainian%20interceptor%20drone%20hunts%20down%20a%20Russian%20Shahed.%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%2FScreengrab%20via%20X%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Holzapfel%20said%20the%20Kreuger-100XR's%20%26quot%3Bfastest-in-class%26quot%3B%20speed%20of%20220%20mph%20can%20still%20give%20it%20an%20edge%20against%20the%20Shahed-136%2C%20which%20typically%20flies%20at%20speeds%20around%20115%20mph.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20aiming%20toward%20the%20Shahed%20scenario%20for%20sure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that's%20why%20we're%20also%20considering%20the%20air%20trail%20scenario%2C%20where%20we'll%20be%20chasing%20Shaheds%20from%20another%20airborne%20platform%20and%20attack%20them%20even%20from%20above.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%20the%20Kreuger-100XR%20could%20intercept%20the%20drones%20during%20their%20terminal%20attack%2C%20though%20it%20would%20be%20harder%20to%20accurately%20strike%20the%20Russian%20drone%20in%20that%20scenario%20because%20of%20their%20higher%20speeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220a74fee2-3bf7-4d81-8b42-6d4b2041a810%5C%22%3ETo%20build%20an%20interceptor%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHolzapfel%20said%20NAD%20is%20completing%20its%20prototyping%20phase%20and%20moving%20toward%20mass%20production.%20Although%20most%20of%20the%20Kreuger-100XR's%20manufacturing%20should%20be%20automated%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20for%20the%20fuselage%20and%20wings%20%E2%80%94%20it%20will%20still%20require%20humans%20for%20some%20assembly%20tasks%2C%20such%20as%20mounting%20the%20explosive%20warhead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENAD%20aims%20to%20establish%20initial%20manufacturing%20operations%20in%20Sweden%2C%20but%20anticipates%20that%20it%20may%20be%20asked%20to%20build%20the%20Kreuger-100XR%20on-site%20for%20foreign%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we're%20in%20Britain%2C%20they%20probably%20want%20to%20have%20Brits%20assembling%20these%2C%26quot%3B%20Holzapfel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20is%20planning%20for%20its%20supply%20chain%20to%20have%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusinesses-cost-moving-supply-chains-out-china-trump-tariff%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elittle%20dependence%20on%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20possible%2C%20sourcing%20off-the-shelf%20components%20from%20manufacturers%20in%20Europe%2C%20North%20America%2C%20Japan%2C%20or%20South%20Korea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20NAD%20makes%20its%20interceptors%20on%20the%20ninth%20floor%20of%20an%20office%20building%20in%20Stockholm%2C%20where%20its%20team%20of%2023%20sits%20among%20a%20mix%20of%203D%20printers%2C%20prototypes%2C%20and%20workshop%20tables.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENestled%20in%20the%20corner%20of%20a%20room%20is%20one%20of%20the%20startup's%20test-launch%20catapults%3A%20a%20few%20metal%20poles%20and%20some%20string.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20workshop%20tables%20with%20tools%20are%20seen%20for%20prototyping%20interceptors.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691ae91389026fbb4d0dc18c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENAD's%20office%20is%20filled%20with%20a%20mix%20of%20workshop%20tables%2C%20machinery%2C%20and%20office%20desks.%3Cp%3EMatthew%20Loh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20its%20founding%20in%20March%202024%2C%20NAD%20initially%20worked%20on%20another%20interceptor.%20The%20Kreuger-100XR's%20predecessor%2C%20the%20Kreuger-100%2C%20is%20a%20propeller-driven%2C%20wingless%20device%20designed%20to%20eliminate%20drones%20solely%20by%20hitting%20them%20in%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it's%20ideally%20suited%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-a-drone%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esmaller%2C%20commercial%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20as%20the%20hobby%20drones%20that%20Ukrainian%20and%20Russian%20troops%20face%20regularly%20on%20the%20front%20lines%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20holds%20the%20Kruger-100%20in%20his%20right%20hand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691ae7db89026fbb4d0dc186%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Kruger-100%20is%20meant%20to%20fit%20in%20one%20hand.%20This%20is%20a%20prototype%20of%20the%20original%20interceptor%2C%20but%20is%20highly%20similar%20in%20appearance%20to%20the%20actual%20product.%3Cp%3EMatthew%20Loh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHolzapfel%20said%20prospective%20clients%20were%20more%20interested%20in%20capabilities%20for%20fighting%20larger%20targets%2C%20such%20as%20Shaheds%2C%20and%20so%20the%20firm%20pivoted%20toward%20the%20XR%20variant%20during%20the%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20NAD%20has%20raised%20about%20%244.4%20million%20and%20is%20looking%20to%20begin%20another%20seed%20round%20early%20next%20year%2C%20he%20added.%20Afterward%2C%20the%20firm%20hopes%20to%20recruit%20software%20engineers%20to%20train%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-army-software-linking-artillery-drones-ai-changing-warfighting-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20can%20manage%20a%20defensive%20swarm.%3