quot%3B20VC%26quot%3B%20podcast%20published%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Altman%20said%20that%20tech%20once%20became%20too%20focused%20on%20prioritizing%20mission%20over%20%26quot%3Bwinning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20say%2C%20don't%20care%20about%20the%20product.%20Don't%20care%20about%20anything%2C%20just%20go%20work%20at%20the%20fastest%20growing%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20venture%20capitalist%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20winning%20feels%20great.%20It%20feels%20amazing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20is%20the%20cofounder%20of%20Saga%2C%20a%20%24125%20million%20venture%20fund%20that%20launched%20last%20March.%20Its%20investments%20include%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalmer-luckey-anduril-china-27-strategy-war-taiwan-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edefense%20tech%20startup%20Anduril%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Reddit%2C%20and%20Rippling.%20He%20is%20the%20younger%20brother%20of%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20and%20the%20older%20brother%20of%20Jack%20Altman%2C%20also%20a%20VC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday's%20podcast%2C%20Max%20Altman%20said%20that%20tech%20lost%20its%20way%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%20before%202020.%20Before%20becoming%20an%20investor%2C%20he%20worked%20at%20Microsoft%2C%20Zenefits%2C%20and%20Rippling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20everyone%20in%20tech%20was%20making%20their%20company%20about%20their%20mission%20and%20%26quot%3Bsaving%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20doing%20on-demand%20dry%20cleaning%20and%20on-demand%20dog%20walking%2C%20but%20it's%20gonna%20help%20the%20world%20this%20way%2C%20and%20you%20should%20feel%20good%20about%20yourself%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20like%2C%20just%20go%20build%20a%20great%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWinning's%20the%20most%20fun%20thing%20here.%20And%20I%20think%20we%20really%20lost%20our%20way%20for%20a%20little%20a%20bit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E