08%2Faloe-vera-1-1723014094.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hrushikesh%20utilises%20aloe%20vera%20to%20make%20natural%20pesticides%2C%20herbal%20spreader%2C%20and%20plant%20growth%20promoter.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-1-1723014094.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-1-1723014094-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-1-1723014094-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-1-1723014094-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-1-1723014094-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360103%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHrushikesh%20uses%20aloe%20vera%20to%20make%20natural%20pesticides%2C%20herbal%20spreaders%2C%20and%20plant%20growth%20promoters.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CPlants%20like%20bananas%20naturally%20avert%20water%20on%20its%20surface.%20It%20becomes%20difficult%20for%20farmers%20to%20spray%20pesticides%20on%20their%20leaves.%20Spraying%20aloe%20vera%20spreader%20helps%20spread%20pesticide%20throughout%20the%20length%20of%20the%20plant.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20Hrushikesh%20started%20commercialising%20these%20products%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20friends%20he%20made%20from%20marketing%20jobs.%20Today%2C%20he%20manufactures%20an%20average%20of%208%2C000%20litres%20of%20products%20from%20his%20aloe%20vera%20farm%2C%20now%20expanded%20to%20two%20acres%20of%20land.%20With%20this%2C%20he%20has%20been%20able%20to%20clock%20an%20annual%20turnover%20of%20Rs%203.5%20crore%2C%20of%20which%2C%20his%20profit%20margin%20is%2030%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20feat%20did%20not%20come%20easy%20to